library(treemap)
data(GNI2014)
qwer <- GNI2014[GNI2014$continent == 'North America', ]

treemap(qwer,
        index = c("continent","iso3"),
        vSize = "population",
        vColor = "population",
        type = "value",
        bg.labels = "yellow",
        title = "North America population ")
